Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A rice ball from a \Nconvenience store would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if it's cold and hardened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd trade 1,000 fish burgers for 1 rice ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If a bowl of freshly cooked rice \Nwere placed before me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am sure tears would flood down \Nfrom my eyes in torrents!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what I truly yearn for is Neko Ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:31.63,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}A world where I can go eat at Neko Ramen, \Nsetting up shop randomly in the middle of the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That world is what I call...
