Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:36.87,Paradise,,0,0,0,,{\fs107\be0.5\bord0\c&H000000&}Ozu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person who brought a castella \Nto most of my rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Participating in many circles, \NI still don't have a full portrait of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From the info I have, he would \Nget in the way of people's love,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}setting off fires and scenes of carnage on a daily basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the disciple of Master Higuchi, \Nhe created an exposé film on Mr. Jougasaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all the while sucking up to Mr. Jougasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And as a double agent, \Nhe dyed Mr. Higuchi's yukata pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before long, as a tool of Aijima,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he was kicked out of the movie circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And this time, entrapping Aijima, he climbed himself to the top of the Secret Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That bulletin board was also Ozu's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While leading his renaissance-man-like campus life, he cheered me on in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and continued to meddle in every one of my lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only I had met him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then I bet my campus life \Nwould have been a fun one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ozu always seemed to be my only real friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This was Ozu's smartphone, \Nwhich he must have forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tried all kinds of passwords.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then for fun, I punched in \NKohinata-san's name, and it unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amazingly, it seems that \NKohinata-san was Ozu's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why didn't he ever introduce her to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it seemed like this was Ozu's big secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ozu asked to borrow the airship that Honwaka had, but he was told no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.55,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}They were tossed around in the crowd of people, \Nand she ended up crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, I can't just do that out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ceremonial fires of Gozan are \Na symbol of the summer nights of Kyoto.
