Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is impossible to see them all \Nfrom the ground at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:27.57,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}But Ozu planned on going on a sightseeing flight \Nto see the Gozan with Kohinata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he an idiot?
