Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.40,Phone,,0,0,0,,{\move(207.098,313.16,207.098,113.086)\be0.6}Wait for me in the top bell tower \Nof the Honwaka Health Facility \Nat 19:50. \N\NI'll come to pick you up in an airship. \N\N\NKeep it a secret from your father \Nand everyone.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.68,0:08:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seemed like Ozu planned on \Ntaking the airship by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm just borrowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a fearfully pure love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An idiot through and through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder where he gets all that boldness from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:45.67,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}Is this really the judgment of a human whose heart \Nis so twisted they are mistaken for a youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are collecting information on this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gozan.
