Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gozan was more than two months \Nafter the day I became lost in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I could escape from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd eat the tarako spaghetti at Café Collection,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd slurp Neko Ramen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd dive into the large tub at the public bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd go see movies at Kawaramachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd haggle with the old \Nbookstore owner on Gabi Street,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd even listen during lecture at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd become Master Higuchi's disciple and engage in ribald storytelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd experience Hanuki-san's endless night of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd help Mr. Jougasaki with his passionate, meaningless films,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd even try dabbling in the Secret Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:46.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though I tried lying to console myself, \Nit became harder and harder every day.
