Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:10:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the room I originally lived in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:04.80,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}Somehow, after these dozens and dozens of days, I had returned to the 4.5-tatami room I started at.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be that the corner of \Nan endless world of 4.5-tatami rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believed so strongly I was traveling through \Nwas in fact a small loop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this the end of the world? Am I dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish I could live happily together with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had thought the days were all wasted, \Nbut they were such a bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always dreaming of the unrealistic,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never looked at what I had right around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the life I chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And this is the result of that wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was early evening at the Shimogamo used book fair the previous summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only a short stretch from my boarding house,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would go there every day, fishing for books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each one is a Mochiguma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All five as a group are called \Nthe Mochiguman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, I have lost one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that point, the girl whose expression was like some European fortress city broke open,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and her smile made an impression that has never left my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In short, frankly, to put it plainly, honestly, saying it without any reservation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I fell head over heels for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:37.46,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}That night, when I went to collect my clothes \Nfrom the laundromat,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my charcoal-colored boxers I had lovingly worn the past two years
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}had been mysteriously switched with this little stuffed fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And although I put it in my pocket \Nintending to give it to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should have thought to look for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I had never taken the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop wandering aimlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and grab that opportunity with all your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll take that step now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whether it takes 100 steps,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or 1,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stay on that side \Nfor the Daimonji Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu, have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You damn traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:49.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got nowhere to run, Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu-senpai, have you done \Nsome more mischief?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:53.11,Mountains,,0,0,0,,{\pos(921.143,171.143)\3c&H0765A5&\bord0.8\blur3\frx23\fry0}Daimonji
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.93,0:13:53.11,Mountains,,0,0,0,,{\pos(921.143,171.143)\c&H0788D4&\bord0\be0.8\frx23\fry0}Daimonji
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you say you're gonna do \Nsomething to me, then I'm jumping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not coming down until \Nyou can guarantee my safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think you're in a position to bargain for your safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think about what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough! I'm jumping!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:53.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're naked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll cover for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moths?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was in the Kyoto newspaper the next day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the sudden outbreak of moths is still not properly understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, I suspect you \Ndear viewers understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He actually fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about we kill him instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the type of guy who wouldn't stay down even if you killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow! My leg is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you go, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you care about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and I are connected by \Nthe black thread of fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're \Ntalking about! And I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu is not going to run away, \Nso calm yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ended up falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I said to "break a leg" for a girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one incorrigible fool, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You reap what you sow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What nerve you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Jougasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you also a resident \Nof Shimogamo Yuusuisou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave Ozu to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cover yourself with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't go by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanuki-san is waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show her you're a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell her "Come with me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're an interesting person, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having failed to steal the airship,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he changed into women's clothes \Nat the suggestion of Master Higuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and returned to Shimogamo \Ndown the canals of Lake Biwa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}where he was supposed to \Nrendezvous with the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the disguise was easily seen through, or rather made him stand out more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:28.88,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}And he was cornered by Honwaka, \Nand members of the Lucky Cat Chinese Restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}plus Mr. Jougasaki who had \Nrealized the betrayal of his disciple,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}plus all manner of people whose love \Nhe had gotten in the way of,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}until he was forced onto the railing of the Kamo Bridge and fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something I once picked up. I believe it is yours, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you be the owner of the mouse-colored boxers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A year ago, when I washed this Mochiguma,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it got switched with some men's underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I've been searching \Nfor their owner ever since!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that underwear... will fit me perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if you'd like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about we go to Neko Ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:21.30,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\t(4030,4880,\c&H000000&)}For some reason, I have a feeling like I've been \Nwaiting for those words for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it really that delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This flavor really is unmatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it is not the purpose of this program
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to show the further development \Nof my relationship with Akashi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will withhold from showing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:40.38,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}I wouldn't want to throw my dear viewer's time \Ndown the gutter, now would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing else is as boring to tell as a story of successful love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was half forced to become Master Higuchi's disciple,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the Master has now disappeared on his journey around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.66,Scrub Brush,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,499.182)\p1\blur1.5\c&HFFFFFF&\alpha&H80&\fscx613\fscy410}m 0 0 l 0 16.625 l 153.375 16.625 l 153.375 0
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.66,Scrub Brush,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,509.219)\be0.8}Do not try this with normal scrub brush
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My regret at becoming his disciple was one of the fastest in history,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but as I pulled the pins out from the globe,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I became entranced imagining \Nwhere Master Higuchi must be now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Jougasaki said he left the laboratory and planned to get a job somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Speaking of which, I wonder where \Nthe wordless beauty "Kaori-san" is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I pray that she and Mr. Jougasaki are \Nleading a happy life together somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one thing Master Higuchi worried about,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the "Masochistic Proxy-Proxy War," was carried on by myself and Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While he was in the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I painted the bicycle he called the "Dark Scorpion" pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To go along with the great change in myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I found a new boarding house in Mototanaka
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and moved there with all haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, I never wanted to spend the night \Nin that 4.5-tatami room ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time, I chose a 6-tatami room and made sure it had its own bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu-san has a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't let that one go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stole the airship in order to \Nlet her see the bonfires from the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even called you all to the Kamo Bridge \Nto show how gallant he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. But he failed, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu-san really hates it when \Nthe conversation turns to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he turns into a good boy \Nwhen he's in front of his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the gang's all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even with all that evil you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you still had time to go out with Kohinata-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What might you be talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that you once called Hanuki-san for advice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when you thought you were \Nbeing dumped. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lies! It's all lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell us all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I invoke my right to remain silent! \NI want a lawyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're having a tough time \Neven while you're in the hospital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you run away somewhere \Nuntil things cool down?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave the expenses to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you plotting? You can't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should try trusting in other people more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are big-hearted people like me \Nin this world, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In exchange, let me meet your girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! I refuse! You're so evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all for your sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why must you be so interested in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the way I show my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can keep that icky love to yourself!

